---
---

<section class="action" id="take-action">
  <div class="action-inner">
    <div class="action-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Take Action</p>
      <h2 class="action-heading">Two calls, five minutes, real change</h2>
      <p class="action-lede">
        Every phone call and every 311 report creates institutional pressure that officials cannot ignore. Here's how you can help right now.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="action-cards">
      <div class="action-card action-card-call reveal">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3>Call Your Council Member</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-list">
          <p class="contact-note">The trail is in Council District B. Contact Councilmember Harris and your own council member.</p>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <span class="contact-district">District B</span>
            <span class="contact-name">Lesli Harris</span>
            <a href="tel:504-658-1020" class="contact-phone">504-658-1020</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <span class="contact-district">At-Large</span>
            <span class="contact-name">JP Morrell</span>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <span class="contact-district">At-Large</span>
            <span class="contact-name">Matthew Willard</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="call-script">
          <h4>What to say:</h4>
          <p>
            "I'm calling to ask that the council allocate bond funds to resurface the Norman C. Francis Parkway trail. It's one of the city's two most-used off-street paths, it's crumbling, and no department has taken responsibility. With Dr. Francis's passing, now is the time to make this path worthy of his legacy."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="action-card action-card-311 reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="action-card-header">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
            <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/>
          </svg>
          <h3>File a 311 Report</h3>
        </div>

        <a href="https://nola311.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="action-311-link">
          <span>Go to nola311.org</span>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6M15 3h6v6M10 14L21 3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>

        <div class="steps-list">
          <h4>How to file effectively:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Categorize as <strong>"pothole / road surface issue"</strong>, not a park complaint. This routes it to DPW, who owns the pavement.</li>
            <li>Include photos of the specific damage: cracks, heaves, root intrusions, gaps.</li>
            <li>Note the cross street and which side of the neutral ground.</li>
            <li>If your report is closed without repair, <strong>refile immediately</strong> and reference the original case number.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-share reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <h3>Spread the Word</h3>
      <p>Share this page with your neighbors, your neighborhood association, and on social media. The more voices, the harder to ignore.</p>
      <button class="share-btn" id="copy-link-btn">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/>
          <path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Copy link to this page</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const btn = document.getElementById('copy-link-btn');
  if (btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      try {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(window.location.href);
        const span = btn.querySelector('span');
        if (span) {
          const original = span.textContent;
          span.textContent = 'Copied!';
          setTimeout(() => { span.textContent = original; }, 2000);
        }
      } catch {
        // Fallback: select text for manual copy
      }
    });
  }
</script>

<style>
  .action {
    background: var(--dark-warm);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .action::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(200, 168, 78, 0.3), transparent);
  }

  .action-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .action-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--ivory);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .action-lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 650px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .action-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .action-card {
    background: var(--dark-surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 168, 78, 0.12);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .action-card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .action-card-header svg {
    color: var(--gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .action-card-header h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ivory);
  }

  .contact-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .contact-note {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ivory);
  }

  .contact-note-secondary {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .contact-district {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(200, 168, 78, 0.1);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .contact-name {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ivory);
  }

  .contact-phone {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    margin-left: auto;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-phone:hover {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .call-script {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    padding-top: 1.2rem;
  }

  .call-script h4 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .call-script p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .action-311-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dark);
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .action-311-link:hover {
    background: var(--gold-light);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .steps-list h4 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .steps-list ol {
    list-style: none;
    counter-reset: steps;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .steps-list li {
    counter-increment: steps;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .steps-list li::before {
    content: counter(steps);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .steps-list li strong {
    color: var(--ivory);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .action-share {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .action-share h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ivory);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .action-share p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .share-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .share-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(200, 168, 78, 0.1);
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .action {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .action-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .action-card {
      padding: 1.8rem;
    }
    .contact-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.2rem;
    }
    .contact-phone {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
